{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59048B1906P2D1N002420", "chronotag": "1762948121916", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "II-CF2420", "numeroOrdreDepot": "2420", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_FIN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59048B1906P2D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B1906", "triAmendement": "eaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaajzace", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA720976", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845485", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA719286", "PA841359", "PA795244", "PA841931", "PA721110", "PA720960", "PA793796", "PA2952"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Mathiasin,  M.&#160;Colombani, Mme&#160;de&#160;P&#233;lichy, M.&#160;Lenormand, M.&#160;Mazaury, Mme&#160;Sanquer, M.&#160;Serva, M.&#160;Taupiac et M.&#160;Warsmann"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "ETAT B", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 49", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 49", "type": "ANNEXE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": "ARTICLE 49", "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/1906C.asp#D_Etat_B"}, "missionVisee": {"codeEtat": "B", "codeMissionMinefi": "OA", "libelleMission": "Outre-mer", "missionRef": "3351"}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositifAmdtCreditPLF": {"listeProgrammes": {"programme": [{"libelle": "Emploi outre-mer", "programmeRef": "653791", "autorisationEngagement": "-2000000", "creditPaiement": "-2000000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Conditions de vie outre-mer", "programmeRef": "653793", "autorisationEngagement": "2000000", "creditPaiement": "2000000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}]}, "soldeAE": "0", "soldeCP": "0", "cpEgalAe": "true"}, "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Cet amendement vise &#x00E0; renforcer les contrats de convergence et de transformation (CCT) afin de mieux accompagner les collectivit&#x00E9;s locales dans leurs projets d&#x2019;investissements structurants sur l'ensemble des territoires ultramarins.</p><p>Aussi est-il propos&#x00E9; :</p><p>- d'augmenter de 2 M&#x20AC; l&#x2019;action 2 &#x00AB; Am&#x00E9;nagement du territoire &#x00BB; du programme Programme 123 &#x2013; Conditions de vie Outre&#x2011;mer,</p><p>- et de diminuer de 2 M&#x20AC;&nbsp;les cr&#x00E9;dits de l&#x2019;action 01 &#x00AB; Soutien aux entreprises &#x00BB; du programme 138 &#x00AB; Emploi Outre-mer &#x00BB;.</p><p>Cette r&#x00E9;duction a pour but de se conformer aux exigences de la loi organique relative aux lois de finances (LOLF) qui oblige, lorsque l&#x2019;auteur d&#x2019;un amendement souhaite augmenter les cr&#x00E9;dits d&#x2019;un programme, &#x00E0; diminuer les cr&#x00E9;dits d&#x2019;un autre programme d&#x2019;autant. Il n&#x2019;est donc en r&#x00E9;alit&#x00E9; pas envisag&#x00E9; de restreindre les moyens allou&#x00E9;s aux entreprises d&#x2019;Outre-mer mais bien d'attribuer de nouveaux moyens &#x00E0; l'am&#x00E9;nagement du territoire.</p><p>En cons&#x00E9;quence, les signataires du pr&#x00E9;sent amendement demandent au Gouvernement de lever le gage.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-11-06", "datePublication": "2025-11-12", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Tomb\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2025-11-12T12:48:16+01:00", "sort": "Tomb\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59048B1906P2D1N002420?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "2", "divisionCodeLoi": "2"}, "discussionCommune": {"idDiscussion": "34655", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "84547", "typePosition": "Dernier"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}